  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dc5\u0dcf\u0dad\u0dca \u0dbb\u0dd0\u0dc3\u0d9a\u0da7  \u0dad\u0daf \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0dc3\u0dd2 \u0dc3\u0db8\u0d9f \u0dc3\u0dd4\u0dc5\u0d82",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Winds with heavy rains in many regions",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Department of Meteorology, an increase in rain and wind conditions in the south-western part of the island, in the western and southern sea areas is expected from today (1) due to the activation of the south-west monsoon.",
        "A spokesperson of the Department of Meteorology said that there will be occasional rains in Western, Sabaragamuwa, North and North-West provinces and in Kandy, Nuwara Eliya, Galle and Matara districts, and heavy rains of more than 100 millimeters may occur in some places.",
        "The spokesperson mentioned that in Uva Province and Ampara District, there will be rains in the evening or at night, and in the western slopes of the Central Highlands and in the Southern Province, winds of up to 50 km/h may occur from time to time.",
        "He said that this situation will continue for a few more days and the sea areas off the coast from Galle through Hambantota to Pothuvil may be very rough.",
        "He said that fast winds of 60, 70 km per hour can occur in those sea areas and sea waves can also rise.",
        "The spokesman said that people engaged in fishing and marine activities in that sea area should be careful.",
        "The department is notifying the people to take measures to avoid accidents as lightning accidents and temporary strong winds may occur along with thunderstorms."
      ],
